        <updateDate>2020-10-26T19:47:44Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Improving Diaper Affordability Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill includes diapers as deductible medical expenses and allows payments for diapers from certain tax-preferred spending and reimbursement accounts. The bill prohibits state or local governments from imposing a sales tax on the retail purchase of diapers. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
